                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 836/122.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Janes</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Rio de Janeiro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1909-01-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 17, 1909</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Reports presidential decree signed 14th, which continues during 1909 tariff
                    reduction of 20 per cent, favoring articles enjoying privilege last year.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
